cleaned_text: Natural Balance Natural Balance Limited Ingredient Reserve Grain Free Sweet Potato & Venison Recipe Dry Dog Food Regular price $53.99 Sometimes what's NOT in your dog's food is just as important as what is. That's the guiding philosophy behind Natural Balance L.I.D. Limited Ingredient Diets Sweet Potato & Venison Formula, a super premium dry dog food made to help feed your dog's greatness. Our sweet potato and venison formula is crafted with purposefully selected ingredients: gluten-free carbohydrate sources to help provide your dog with energy and a single source of animal protein to help maintain strong, lean muscle. What you won't find on our carefully crafted ingredients list are fillers, added corn, wheat or soy, or artificial flavors, colors or preservatives. Everything is chosen to provide a complete and balanced diet that helps support the nutritional needs of adult dogs big and small. Turns out the simplest choice is all you need to feed your dog with confidence!
